data.text: Thass my lil rant since my daughter is not feeling good and doesnt want to sleep 😭
Anywayzzz i think they gonna be bomb ass parents👨‍👩‍👧 i mean who wouldnt want @KylieJenner & @Travisscott as their parents
Also bitch do you kno how hard it is to keep something like that a secret?? I waited the WHOLE nine months until i told everyone and it was probably one of the hardest things ive ever had to do
I mean obviously its different situations but i can definitely relate to her wanting it to be private. Pregnancy is a so special there is no room for hate🙅🏻‍♀️
I didnt go to the lengths @KylieJenner did to hide her pregnancy but i didnt wanna announce it bc i didnt want the stress and mixed emotions from the people who would be unsupportive
